 <br>
Dilution of the traditionalists (Pre May-8th) continues,and in the end,RPing will be exactly what it is on every other server.<br>
 <br>
A curiousity. A freakish one,at that.<br>
 <br>
What remains allows for slightly more polite play than most blue servers,simply because with only one character per account,there is no &quot;alt&quot; to hide on or start over with.<br>
 <br>
Roleplay,to truly work on a large scale REQUIRES artificial limitations that change a world from the &quot;norm&quot; and create worlds that do not conform to reality.<br>
 <br>
Teir'dal are evil. Iksar are xenophobic. Paladins of Mithaniel Marr are goodie-two-shoes. And so on.<br>
 <br>
